Edit: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/10068 is merged

@aselle I think all my changes are done for this PR, please continue the review process. This op now allows users to specify the axis. I also added one test case to test when `axis != 0` and one test case to test when `rank > 2`. All these tests pass on my machine.

This PR relies on https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/10032 that has not been merged into master branch yet. I manually merge them into this branch to make this work. So you don't have to worry about changes in `shape_inference.cc` and `cuda_kernel_helper.h` because they are reviewed separately. You may not want to merge this before these two dependencies are merged.
